## ADVANCED USERS

hc scaffold web-app --ui vue forum
# Scaffolds an empty web-app (without DNAs)
# At the end it says: "Start to create DNAs with hc scaffold dna forum"

hc scaffold dna forum

hc scaffold zome posts --dna forum
# Scaffolds both integrity and coordinator

hc scaffold integrity-zome posts_integrity --dna forum
hc scaffold coordinator-zome posts --dependencies posts_integrity --dna forum

hc scaffold entry-def post
# Prompt: Which DNA? Selector of DNAs

hc scaffold entry-def post # works if you only have one DNA and one zome
# Scaffold UI components

hc scaffold entry-def post --dna forum --zome posts --field title:String --field content:String --read false --update false --delete false

hc scaffold index-globally post --dna forum --zome posts
# If you have a "create_post" function, just add the create_link at the end of it
# If not, ask the developer: Which function is creating the post?

hc scaffold index-by-author post --link-to-entry-hash --dna forum --zome posts
hc scaffold index-by-time post --link-to-entry-hash --dna forum --zome posts

hc scaffold entry-def comment --field comment:String --dna forum --zome posts
hc scaffold link-type posts comments  --dna forum --zome posts
# Add link_type
# get_comments_for_post(action_hash) -> Vec<Record>
